The First Ward of Dover gives Cheney 193; Marcy, 95. The First Ward of Concord gives Cheney 211; Marcy, 170. The Second, Fourth, and Seventh Wards of Portsmouth give Cheney 419; Marcy, 338. These returns show Republican gains.
